Package com.ibm.websphere.ras.annotation

Annotation Type ManualTrace

@Retention(RUNTIME) @Target({TYPE,METHOD}) public @interface ManualTrace
This annotation indicates that a method has been detected to have manual trace and should not have additional trace added automatically. This annotation is not intended to be added manually.
